level.text:
Vocational and other training services, including personal and vocational adjustment training, books, tools, and other training materials, except that no training or training services in an institution of higher education (universities, colleges,
        community or junior colleges, vocational schools, technical institutes, or hospital schools of nursing) may be paid for with funds under this part unless maximum efforts have been made by the Rehabilitation Services Administration and the individual
        to secure grant assistance in whole or in part from other sources to pay for that training;
